---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="桌面版 — Electron + Vue3 打造的本地 AI 工作台 | ChainlessChain"
  description="ChainlessChain 桌面版 v5.0.2.43：Electron 39 + Vue 3.4 + TypeScript，V6 Chat-First Shell（P0–P6 完成）+ `/v6-preview` Claude-Desktop 预览壳（P7–P9c · 4 主题 + 4 颗去中心化入口 + 真 LLM 桥 + 流式 composer）+ 139 内置 Skills、RAG 知识库、Plan Mode、Instinct 学习、51 Pinia stores。Windows / macOS / Linux 全平台。"
  canonical="https://www.chainlesschain.com/desktop"
>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-paper opacity-60 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="container-wide relative pt-20 pb-20 md:pt-28 md:pb-24">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="chip mb-6 animate-fade-in">DESKTOP · v5.0.2.43</div>
        <h1 class="animate-fade-in-delay font-display text-6xl md:text-display-lg leading-[1.02]">
          Electron + Vue3<br/>打造的<span class="italic text-ember">本地 AI 工作台</span>。
        </h1>
        <p class="animate-fade-in-delay-2 mt-8 text-xl text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
          不是浏览器套壳，不是 web 包装。原生文件系统访问、硬件 U-Key 直连、本地 Ollama 深度集成 —
          GUI 该有的体验，Electron 该给的性能。
        </p>
        <div class="animate-fade-in-delay-3 mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="#download" class="btn-ember">下载桌面版 ↓</a>
          <a href="/cli" class="btn-ghost">偏好命令行？</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Hero screenshot -->
  <section class="pb-16">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <figure class="border border-ink/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl bg-paper">
        <img
          src="/screenshots/dashboard.png"
          alt="ChainlessChain 桌面版 · 主面板"
          width="1400"
          height="900"
          loading="eager"
          class="block w-full h-auto"
        />
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-12 max-w-3xl">不是更多功能，是更合适的功能。</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          ['139', '内置 Skills', '代码审查、文档生成、医疗分诊、法律起草 — 装完即用。'],
          ['RAG', '语义检索', 'BM25 + TF-IDF + Qdrant 向量混合检索，精度与召回双优。'],
          ['Plan', 'Plan Mode', '先生成计划、经你审批、再动文件。高风险操作不打扰。'],
          ['Instinct', 'Instinct 学习', '从你的修改、提问、选择中自动学会偏好，越用越贴合。'],
          ['51', 'Pinia Stores', '精细拆分的状态层，每一块数据都有它的归属。'],
          ['MCP', '外部工具生态', '文件系统、Git、SQLite 等主流 MCP 服务器开箱可用。'],
        ].map(([tag, title, desc]) => (
          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-line hover:border-ember transition-colors">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-ember mb-3">{tag}</div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl mb-3">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Screenshot grid -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-cream/50 border-y border-line">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-10">功能预览</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          ['chat', 'AI 对话 · 流式响应'],
          ['cowork', 'Web Cowork · 任务自动化'],
          ['skills', 'Skills 系统 · 139 项内置技能'],
        ].map(([file, caption]) => (
          <figure class="border border-ink/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl bg-paper">
            <img
              src={`/screenshots/${file}.png`}
              alt={caption}
              width="1400"
              height="900"
              loading="lazy"
              class="block w-full h-auto"
            />
            <figcaption class="px-4 py-3 text-xs text-muted border-t border-line font-mono">{caption}</figcaption>
          </figure>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Download -->
  <section id="download" class="py-24">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12">
        <div class="chip mb-6">下载 · v5.0.2.43</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight">三大平台，同一份体验。</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          ['Windows', 'win', '.exe · 约 120MB', '支持 Win 10+ · U-Key 原生驱动'],
          ['macOS', 'mac', '.dmg · Intel / Apple Silicon', 'macOS 12+ · 模拟模式'],
          ['Linux', 'linux', '.AppImage · x86_64', 'Ubuntu 20.04+ · 模拟模式'],
        ].map(([name, key, meta, note]) => (
          <a href="https://github.com/chainlesschain/chainlesschain/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-line hover:border-ember hover:bg-ember/5 transition-all block">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted mb-3">{key.toUpperCase()}</div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-3xl mb-2 group-hover:text-ember transition-colors">{name}</h3>
            <div class="text-sm text-ink mb-3">{meta}</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-muted">{note}</div>
            <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-ember opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">下载安装包 ↓</div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-muted text-center">
        开发者偏好命令行？试试 <code class="font-mono bg-cream px-2 py-0.5 rounded">npm i -g chainlesschain</code>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
